author: hwright
msg: Fix issue #3187.  Fix reverse merges where merge target or subtree
has non-inheritable revision ranges intersecting with the merged
range.  Not a common use case, but completely broken without this
r30888 is just a revert of some accidental whitespace changes
in r30883.  This group changes the svn_rangelist_intersect API.
If this group isn't backported for 1.5.0 it needs to be
reverted on trunk and svn_rangelist_intersect() revved.
